@startuml
title Post Answer Sequence Diagram

actor User

participant AnswerController
participant IAnswerService
participant AnswerServiceImpl
participant UserRepo
participant QuestionRepo
participant AnswerRepo
database Database

User -> AnswerController : Submit Answer
AnswerController -> IAnswerService : addAnswer(dto)
IAnswerService -> AnswerServiceImpl : addAnswer(dto)

AnswerServiceImpl -> UserRepo : findById(userId)
UserRepo -> Database : SELECT User

AnswerServiceImpl -> QuestionRepo : findById(questionId)
QuestionRepo -> Database : SELECT Question

AnswerServiceImpl -> AnswerRepo : save(answer)
AnswerRepo -> Database : INSERT Answer

Database --> AnswerRepo : Answer
AnswerRepo --> AnswerServiceImpl : Saved Answer
AnswerServiceImpl --> AnswerController : Success
AnswerController --> User : Answer Posted

@enduml